title: Person Of Interest Soundtrack   The Machine Theme Compilation
author: EPICX
comment: Most underrated series of all time. Wish it didn't end soon

This show evolved into something that ended up become much greater than what I believe it set out to do. From a cop chasing a “Man in a suit” to asking the greater questions about the morality of giving up freedom and privacy for safety and security. Masterpiece.
Mr Rees is a combination of James bond and batman.
I can't stop listening to this, terribly addictive
One of the most amazing themes in television history
